{"title":"花环（外一首）","authors":["高缨"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":9,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"花环（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高缨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花环"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给泰国作家朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要凋残，你这美丽的花环，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要失去色彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也莫把馨香消散。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你虽然很小、很小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仅仅套住我的手腕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是我无比地喜爱你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜过一座花园；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为你每一片花瓣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都凝结泰国友人的真诚祝愿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，呵，你这美丽的花环，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么偏偏要枯萎凋残！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天天失去幽香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天天损去光艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心为你而忧伤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是我决不离弃你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把你放在枕边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了去寻觅梦——一个童话似的梦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦里的花环越变越大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵朵鲜花串成长长的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里遥，万里远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从曼谷到北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把中泰人民的心紧紧相连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——写在湄南河上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那孩子正向我招手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着淡绿色的水波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的呼喊声被风吹走了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身影也渐渐地隐没。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站在船栏边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥遥挥手答礼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看不清他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他看不清我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是谁呀，可爱的泰国孩子？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从心里呼唤——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你呀，你的名字叫湄南河！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那姑娘在小桥边汲水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着一片青青的水浮莲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的目光向我投来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唇边有淡淡的笑涡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站在船栏边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默地点头问候。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看清了她，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她看清了我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是谁呀，美丽的泰国姊妹？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她悄悄转身，没有回答，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是我知道，我知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的名字叫湄南河！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那阿婆在高脚屋上歇息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旁是菩提树的密叶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她静静地嚼着槟榔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白发映入河上的光波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站在船栏边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虔诚地双手合十。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心里有她，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她心里有我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慈祥的泰国母亲，你是谁呀？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有回答，也不必回答，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我知道，我知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的名字，叫湄南河！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}